    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click and create small balls. Progress and earn money. Unlock new features. It's great fun to earn money for free.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329000/extras/b4a70d717d72b1bdcb94e952d1b05be8.poster.avif?t=1734120006\" width=572 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329000/extras/b4a70d717d72b1bdcb94e952d1b05be8.webm?t=1734120006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329000/extras/b4a70d717d72b1bdcb94e952d1b05be8.mp4?t=1734120006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Pure Water system creates bottles that will be your target as you create balls. Bottles offer more money and a more fun structure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329000/extras/bb84e1cbaa720362d7cde2ea982008e7.poster.avif?t=1734120006\" width=572 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329000/extras/bb84e1cbaa720362d7cde2ea982008e7.webm?t=1734120006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329000/extras/bb84e1cbaa720362d7cde2ea982008e7.mp4?t=1734120006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you need a manager? Then there will be a person waiting for you. You can hire him and have him create balls for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329000/extras/5613eeb23eb9e033774bc4d3af657d0f.poster.avif?t=1734120006\" width=572 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329000/extras/5613eeb23eb9e033774bc4d3af657d0f.webm?t=1734120006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329000/extras/5613eeb23eb9e033774bc4d3af657d0f.mp4?t=1734120006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to check the prize bags at short intervals. There will be more prizes in your chest in these bags! In the final, a very special creature will be waiting for you.</p>",
